      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普反弹暂停，美国股市震荡：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在标准普尔 500 指数连续三天历史性飙升后，交易员暂停交易，导致美国股指期货出现波动。在中国刺激计划令投资者失望后，油价随亚洲市场下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:14:05 GMT</pubDate>
